ROCm decode: matmul_f16 audit results — 10 ms/tok, ~6 ms recoverable

Status: AUDITED 2026-05-09 (was tsk-37 audit). Real per-shape GPU+sync time captured via DS4_ROCM_SYNC_EACH=1 DS4_ROCM_AUDIT_F16=1 ./ds4 -n 50.

Per-shape breakdown (decode only, n_tok=1):
  shape       calls/tok   us/call   GiB/s_eff   ms/tok   % of 190 GiB/s ceiling
  4096x1024       41         82       95          3.36     50%
